{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"21d21ae7e9","title":"中央关于军事系统大贪污犯公审办法的指示！","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"31a2531183","index":0,"year":1952,"month":3,"day":2,"articleId":"21d21ae7e9"}],"tags":[{"id":"2d13338754","name":"指示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji31","name":"毛泽东全集第31卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/31-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji31":{"comments":[{"id":"e932fed997","publicationId":"maoquanji31","articleId":"21d21ae7e9","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"中共中央中南局1952年3月1日给中央并周恩来的电报中说，拟于3月10日以前召开一次包括中南局、湖北省、武汉市和中南军区4个系统公审大资污分子大会，打算对7至9名大贪污分子分别给以死刑、死刑缓刑、徒刑、徒刑缓刑、释放等处理，借以推动目前正在紧张进行的打虎运动。"}],"contents":[{"id":"2689a2d048","type":"title","text":"中央关于军事系统大资污犯公审办法的指示","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji31","articleId":"21d21ae7e9"},{"id":"e932fed997","type":"paragraph","text":"各中央局、大军区：","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji31","articleId":"21d21ae7e9"},{"id":"84404e6d8f","type":"paragraph","text":"军事系统的大贪污犯不要单独举行公审，要由中央局和大行【政】区政府主持统一举行公审。此种公审有一次即够。公审名单先报周总理批准。中南局三月一日电所说办法”，各大区可以仿行。","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji31","articleId":"21d21ae7e9"},{"id":"10f73a59a7","type":"paragraph","text":"中央","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji31","articleId":"21d21ae7e9"},{"id":"c8944f613e","type":"paragraph","text":"三月二日","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji31","articleId":"21d21ae7e9"}],"page":{"id":"299b270b5d","publicationId":"maoquanji31","articleId":"21d21ae7e9","start":464,"end":464}}}},"__N_SSG":true}